，警察局的警车。后来通过网友互动，把不同的物品放在不同的位置。网友视频中可见，在 2021 年找到了 2027 年「哈维尔」放置的物品。但不同的是，「哈维尔」视频中仍然只有他自己，而网友的视频中则是正常的。6 月 20 日「哈维尔」发布视频，视频中询问一个智能音箱今天几号，回答是 2027 年 6 月 20 日周日。 请问各大网友，该系列视频真实性如何？是否真的存在穿越可能？如果为假，有哪些破绽？哈维尔穿越 2027 视频引全球网友关注，有哪些 BUG？_ 详细解读 _ 最新资讯 _ 热点事件 _36 氪"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-5561ba5c6741ba759ce2bd20d2e16a10_720w.jpg?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "35 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/466675842"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I//LG37OZ5ohTEAMaCDY1OTg1MDczIOD1yIYGMF84lhBAKXIJNDY2Njc1ODQyeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "42_1625299356.6136844", "card_id": "Q_465328241", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 105}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "为什么武磊在一个西乙联赛待了一年比在国内顶级联赛待的人意识和实力高出那么多？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic4.zhimg.com/80/v2-a54ee5fe2d2a126a8158103561d1e4c5_qhd.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "35 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/465328241"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I//LG37OZ5ohTEAMaCDY1Njg1Njk0IIyupoYGMBA4zwNAKnIJNDY1MzI4MjQxeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "43_1625299356.6140575", "card_id": "Q_468326994", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 242}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "当别人说你胖说你丑的时候真的有必要在意人家的看法吗？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-ee5f0999095795b52ab9503ad7121b02_720w.jpg?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "35 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/468326994"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I//LG37OZ5ohTEAMaCDY2MzUyNDQ0IM3O4oYGMAE4pgJAK3IJNDY4MzI2OTk0eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_l